generated_doNotEdit.title: Swim Navigation
generated_doNotEdit.description: Allows this entity to generate paths that include water.

fields.title: Avoid Damage Blocks
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder to avoid blocks that cause damage when finding a path

fields.title: Avoid Portals
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder to avoid portals (like nether portals) when finding a path

fields.title: Avoid Sun
fields.description: Whether or not the pathfinder should avoid tiles that are exposed to the sun when creating paths

fields.title: Avoid Water
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder to avoid water when creating a path

fields.title: Blocks To Avoid
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder which blocks to avoid when creating a path

fields.title: Can Breach
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can jump out of water (like a dolphin)

fields.title: Can Break Doors
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder that it can path through a closed door and break it

fields.title: Can Jump
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can jump up blocks

fields.title: Can Open Doors
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder that it can path through a closed door assuming the AI will open the door

fields.title: Can Open Iron Doors
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder that it can path through a closed iron door assuming the AI will open the door

fields.title: Can Pass Doors
fields.description: Whether a path can be created through a door

fields.title: Can Path From Air
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder that it can start pathing when in the air

fields.title: Can Path Over Lava
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can travel on the surface of the lava

fields.title: Can Path Over Water
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can travel on the surface of the water

fields.title: Can Sink
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it will be pulled down by gravity while in water

fields.title: Can Swim
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can path anywhere through water and plays swimming animation along that path

fields.title: Can Walk
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can walk on the ground outside water

fields.title: Can Walk In Lava
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can travel in lava like walking on ground

fields.title: Is Amphibious
fields.description: Tells the pathfinder whether or not it can walk on the ground underwater
